Package: TCRanker
Type: Package
Title: Rank TCRs by clonotypes for their level in a certain state
Version: 0.1.4
Authors@R: 
    person("Changsheng", "Li", , "changsheng.li@tutanota.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8968-3156"))
Description: A Continuous quantifying algorithm of TCR clonotypes. It Calculates clonal scores of all different clonotypes for their level in a certain state, exhaustion level by default, and provides their final ranking. The ranking state could be customized by providing corresponding gene signature.
